hello，
In the list_page method, the correct situation should be to print out the values stored in the login_page method。
But it prints the original value, Why this can happen?

```python
from pyspider.libs.base_handler import *
import time, string, platform

class Handler(BaseHandler):
    crawl_config = {
        'headers': {
            'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_9_3) AppleWebKit/537.75.14 (KHTML, like Gecko)'
            }
    }   

    # 用于抓取json的cookie，登录操作之后会重新赋值
    __crawl_cookie_json = {'a': 1, 'b': 2}

    @every(minutes= 240)
    def on_start(self):
        self.crawl('https://baidu.com', callback=self.login_page)
 
    @config(age= 60)
    def login_page(self, response):
        #将登录后的cookie进行保存
        self.__crawl_cookie_json = response.cookies
        print self.__crawl_cookie_json
       
        self.crawl('https://baidu.com', callback=self.list_page)

    @config(age= 2 * 60 * 60)
    def list_page(self, response):
        print self.__crawl_cookie_json
```

