Hello,
I'm trying to get a confidence in a multiclass SVM, with 5 class.
For now, i'am using ovo trainer like this :

```
typedef dlib::matrix<double, 2278, 1> sample_type;

typedef dlib::linear_kernel<sample_type> main_kernel;
typedef dlib::svm_c_trainer<main_kernel> main_trainer;

typedef dlib::one_vs_one_trainer<dlib::any_trainer<sample_type>> ovo_trainer;
