As far as compatibility is concerned, as far as I can tell, the mixins use at least one feature which appeared in LESS version 1.7 of less (2014-02-27), namely rulesets.

Even though I already saw issues #5918 and #2695 which might tangentially related I would like to know if you think that something like those would be a good addition to the current font-awesome library.

Best regards,
Rico Moorman

